<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>177</hymn_number>
<title>VAN THURO, THIANG THLARAU, TUM TUAN CH177</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Van Thuro, Thiang Thlarau, tum tuah, Na thawnnak thazang he, Dawtnak
 mei thiang kan kaupiak tuah, Kan lung kikdai chungah.

[V2]
 Lung tho loin hla kan sa tawn, Kan zuamnak a lo dih, Kan kaa in
 Ho-sa-na a dai, Kan dawtnak a ziam cang.

[V3]
 Bawipa, hi bangin a zungzal, Kan nung kho bal lai maw? Kan in dawtnak
 a tlawm, a der, Na dawtnak a ngan ko.

[V4]
 Van thuro, Thiang Thlarau, tum tuah, Na thawnnak thazang he, Kan
 dawtnak mei alhter awk ca, Khamhbawi dawtnak thanh ko.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
</song>